statements: SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData;
SELECT training_id, input_data, output_data FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData WHERE training_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData ORDER BY training_timestamp DESC;
SELECT training_id, input_data, output_data, training_timestamp FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData WHERE training_timestamp >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT training_id, output_data, input_data FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData WHERE output_data LIKE '%success%';
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData ORDER BY training_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT training_id, input_data, output_data FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData WHERE training_id BETWEEN 100 AND 200 ORDER BY training_id ASC;
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData WHERE output_data LIKE '%success%' AND input_data IS NOT NULL;
SELECT training_id, output_data FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData WHERE training_timestamp > '2022-01-01' AND output_data NOT LIKE '%error%' ORDER BY training_timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT training_id, output_data, training_timestamp FROM NeuralNetworkTrainingData WHERE input_data IS NULL ORDER BY training_id ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkModels;
SELECT model_name, input_size FROM NeuralNetworkModels ORDER BY model_name DESC;
SELECT model_name, output_size FROM NeuralNetworkModels WHERE input_size > 100;
SELECT * FROM TrainingData WHERE created_at > '2022-01-01';
SELECT model_id, COUNT(*) AS training_data_count FROM TrainingData GROUP BY model_id;
SELECT model_name, input_size, output_size FROM NeuralNetworkModels;
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkModels WHERE model_id = 3;
SELECT model_name, input_size FROM NeuralNetworkModels ORDER BY input_size ASC;
SELECT model_name, output_size FROM NeuralNetworkModels WHERE model_id > 2 ORDER BY output_size DESC;
SELECT * FROM NeuralNetworkModels JOIN TrainingData ON NeuralNetworkModels.model_id = TrainingData.model_id;
SELECT * FROM training_data ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT label, data FROM training_data WHERE label LIKE '%positive%';
SELECT model_id, learning_rate, epoch FROM model_parameters ORDER BY learning_rate ASC;
SELECT * FROM model_logs WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND loss < 0.5;
SELECT data->>'key1' AS key1_data, data->>'key2' AS key2_data FROM training_data;
SELECT * FROM model_parameters WHERE epoch > 10 ORDER BY learning_rate DESC;
SELECT id, data->>'name' AS name, label FROM training_data WHERE label = 'positive' ORDER BY id;
SELECT model_id, learning_rate, layers FROM model_parameters WHERE layers < 5 ORDER BY model_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM model_logs WHERE loss < 0.1 ORDER BY timestamp ASC;
SELECT training_data.id, training_data.label, model_logs.loss FROM training_data JOIN model_logs ON training_data.id = model_logs.model_id ORDER BY model_logs.loss ASC;
SELECT * FROM TrainingData ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT input_data, target_data FROM TrainingData WHERE id = 1;
SELECT model_name, accuracy FROM NeuralNetworkModels WHERE layers < 5;
SELECT * FROM TrainingLogs WHERE training_time > 1000 ORDER BY training_loss ASC;
SELECT model_name, learning_rate, batch_size FROM NeuralNetworkModels INNER JOIN Hyperparameters ON NeuralNetworkModels.model_id = Hyperparameters.model_id ORDER BY learning_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM TrainingData;
SELECT model_id, model_name FROM NeuralNetworkModels ORDER BY accuracy DESC;

SELECT model_name, training_input FROM training_data WHERE id = 1;

SELECT * FROM model_history WHERE model_id = 3 ORDER BY epoch ASC;
